OL,3,CIs working from home to blame for
OL,4,Cpub's closure?
OL,6,FA landlord has blamed people working
OL,7,Ffrom home as the reason why his pub
OL,8,Fhas been forced to close.
OL,10,FJeremy Brunning, who runs basement pub
OL,11,FThe Henry Potts in Chester, said the
OL,12,Fcity had turned into a "ghost town" as
OL,13,Fnobody was coming in to go to offices
OL,14,Fanymore.
OL,16,FReferencing working from home and
OL,17,F"ridiculous electricity bills", he
OL,18,Fsaid it was "with great sadness and
OL,19,Fnot a little irritation" that the pub
OL,20,Fwas closing.
