OL,3,CIs working from home to blame for
OL,4,Cpub's closure?
OL,6,FMr Brunning said: "I think we'd easily
OL,7,Fhave been able to make it if more
OL,8,Fpeople were in their offices and keen
OL,9,Ffor lunch and early evening
OL,10,Frefreshment, but most seem to be
OL,11,Fworking from home.
OL,13,F"The commercial heart of Chester is a
OL,14,Fbit of a ghost town."
OL,16,FIn the statement, he continued: "It's
OL,17,Fa beautiful pub, like a cosy little
OL,18,Funderground hideaway with excellent
OL,19,Fstaff and the best quality food and
OL,20,Fdrink.
