OL,3,CIs working from home to blame for
OL,4,Cpub's closure?
OL,6,F"However, it's simply not doing enough
OL,7,Ftrade. If you saw the numbers they'd
OL,8,Flook like a lot but in today's
OL,9,Feconomic environment, with ridiculous
OL,10,Felectricity bills and a host of other
OL,11,Finflationary costs, it needs to be
OL,12,Fbusier to be viable.
OL,14,F"So we must close. We'd like to say a
OL,15,Fhuge thank you to the pub's hard-
OL,16,Fworking team.
OL,18,F"They've made us very proud and we are
OL,19,Fdoing what we can to keep and relocate
OL,20,Fthose who want to."
