OL,3,CIs working from home to blame for
OL,4,Cpub's closure?
OL,6,FThe firm behind the pub, Pubs Limited,
OL,7,Falso runs other Cheshire pubs The Hare
OL,8,Fin Farndon, The Black Bear in
OL,9,FWhitchurch, The Swan in Marbury as
OL,10,Fwell as The Druid Inn in Flintshire.
OL,12,FMr Brunning, director of Pubs Limited,
OL,13,Fsaid The Henry Potts had been offered
OL,14,Ffor sale but had so far received "no
OL,15,Fbites".
OL,17,FThe venue will instead be mothballed
OL,18,F"for the foreseeable future".
