OL,3,CIs working from home to blame for
OL,4,Cpub's closure?
OL,6,F"It's such a shame," Mr Brunning
OL,7,Fadded. "If you have enjoyed The Potts
OL,8,Fthen thank you, and sorry to be the
OL,9,Fbearer of bad news. You'll be pleased
OL,10,Fto hear that our other four pubs are
OL,11,Fthriving, so why not go to one of
OL,12,Fthose instead. A nice thing to do if
OL,13,Fyou're WFH (there's an irony)."
